    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This collector-grade E46 M3 is a mechanical masterpiece, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with its high-revving individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS system functioning to factory specifications. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory M-variable differential lock. The chassis remains taut with no subframe fatigue, riding on a perfectly damped suspension setup. This example boasts a pristine exterior with zero oxidation on the Shadowline trim and an interior featuring supple, unblemished Nappa leather. Every toggle, from the DSC to the Sport mode mapping, operates with tactile precision. An uncompromising specimen for the discerning purist seeking a turnkey analog experience.",
